1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:33,280
=Episode 28=
(Pure love defies fate.)

3
00:00:43,100 --> 00:00:44,260
Is it really gone?

4
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:45,660
It's gone!

5
00:00:46,260 --> 00:00:48,019
It's really gone!

6
00:00:48,020 --> 00:00:51,460
Thank goodness!

7
00:00:52,460 --> 00:00:54,779
Thank goodness!

8
00:00:54,780 --> 00:00:57,430
(Ningtai Gate)

9
00:01:00,940 --> 00:01:04,819
(Ningtai Gate)
Thank goodness!

10
00:01:04,820 --> 00:01:06,580
We're safe now!

11
00:01:16,980 --> 00:01:18,140
Zhao...

12
00:01:18,300 --> 00:01:19,380
Xi.

13
00:01:22,020 --> 00:01:23,540
You're still alive.

14
00:01:27,340 --> 00:01:28,780
Thank goodness.

15
00:01:32,020 --> 00:01:34,300
I changed your fate.

16
00:01:35,580 --> 00:01:36,820
From now on,

17
00:01:37,780 --> 00:01:39,540
take care of yourself.

18
00:01:40,380 --> 00:01:42,100
Take care of Baobao too.

19
00:01:43,220 --> 00:01:45,900
We'll... We'll meet again
in the next life.

20
00:01:50,740 --> 00:01:51,900
Dummy,

21
00:01:53,740 --> 00:01:55,460
I'm not letting you die.

22
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:08,180
What are you doing, Zhao?

23
00:02:09,580 --> 00:02:11,980
Zhao, what are you doing?

24
00:02:12,380 --> 00:02:13,460
No!

25
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:16,060
Stop right now!

26
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:20,900
If you give me
your divine heart, you'll die!

27
00:02:22,140 --> 00:02:23,340
Zhao!

28
00:02:35,580 --> 00:02:37,340
No!

29
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:42,540
You still have your people to protect.

30
00:02:42,980 --> 00:02:45,060
And Baobao still needs you.

31
00:02:45,420 --> 00:02:46,620
All I want

32
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:49,620
is to keep you safe.

33
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,380
Zhao!

34
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:55,739
No!

35
00:02:55,740 --> 00:02:56,819
No!

36
00:02:56,820 --> 00:02:58,060
Zhao!

37
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:00,660
You're a god!

38
00:03:01,620 --> 00:03:02,819
If you die,

39
00:03:02,820 --> 00:03:04,820
what happens to your people?

40
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:06,420
I'm begging you!

41
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:08,659
Take your divine heart back,

42
00:03:08,660 --> 00:03:10,140
alright?

43
00:03:12,980 --> 00:03:14,740
What about my people?

44
00:03:14,900 --> 00:03:16,540
They have nothing to do with me.

45
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:21,000
In this world,

46
00:03:24,340 --> 00:03:26,700
you are my god.

47
00:03:31,140 --> 00:03:32,820
We always

48
00:03:34,780 --> 00:03:36,740
meet in winter.

49
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:38,380
But

50
00:03:38,900 --> 00:03:41,260
every winter ends

51
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:43,100
with spring.

52
00:03:43,540 --> 00:03:45,860
When we meet again,

53
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:51,300
I want us...

54
00:03:52,780 --> 00:03:54,100
to...

55
00:03:55,420 --> 00:03:57,380
see...

56
00:04:00,620 --> 00:04:02,300
spring together.

57
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:30,740
Zhao!

58
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:33,859
Come back!

59
00:04:33,860 --> 00:04:36,020
Come back to me!

60
00:04:39,260 --> 00:04:40,580
No!

61
00:04:40,660 --> 00:04:42,460
No!

62
00:04:51,740 --> 00:04:53,820
Again and again...

63
00:04:54,740 --> 00:04:56,859
Again and again!

64
00:04:56,860 --> 00:04:59,140
Again and again!

65
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:04,300
Why?

66
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:08,890
I only wanted Zhao!

67
00:05:38,740 --> 00:05:40,540
Curse you, heavens!

68
00:05:40,980 --> 00:05:43,540
Is this the ending you wanted?

69
00:05:44,660 --> 00:05:45,860
How dare you!

70
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:48,300
You really don't know your place!

71
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:51,539
I'm just a mortal.

72
00:05:51,540 --> 00:05:53,539
Of course I don't know
how high the heavens are

73
00:05:53,540 --> 00:05:55,060
or how deep the earth is!

74
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:57,420
Get out here!

75
00:06:03,420 --> 00:06:05,820
M... Master?

76
00:06:15,860 --> 00:06:16,980
Xi,

77
00:06:17,340 --> 00:06:19,060
I'm leaving on a long journey.

78
00:06:19,220 --> 00:06:22,179
I'll leave Baihua Hall in your care.

79
00:06:22,180 --> 00:06:24,380
When will you come back, Master?

80
00:06:24,540 --> 00:06:26,100
Look at this little plant.

81
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:28,619
It has been growing here
for almost a thousand years.

82
00:06:28,620 --> 00:06:30,180
When it finally blooms,

83
00:06:30,540 --> 00:06:32,300
that is when I'll return.

84
00:06:33,300 --> 00:06:34,500
This jade whistle is for you.

85
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:36,060
Keep it safe.

86
00:06:39,940 --> 00:06:41,380
I will, Master.

87
00:06:41,620 --> 00:06:42,980
Safe travels, Master.

88
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,560
(Qingxin Pavilion)
Travel safe!

89
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:54,740
Hua Hui was born from Ye Zhao's
beast nature after his ascension.

90
00:06:55,180 --> 00:06:56,940
She was born because of him.

91
00:06:57,220 --> 00:06:59,180
So she'll die because of him too.

92
00:06:59,300 --> 00:07:01,219
After all these years,

93
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:02,660
it is finally complete.

94
00:07:03,620 --> 00:07:04,980
Complete?

95
00:07:06,100 --> 00:07:08,180
What kind of completion is this?

96
00:07:08,220 --> 00:07:09,419
You treated us like

97
00:07:09,420 --> 00:07:11,619
pawns you could toy with at will!

98
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:13,539
Our love, hate, rage, and obsession...

99
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:14,980
Our struggle to live or die...

100
00:07:15,100 --> 00:07:17,620
To you, it was all just a game!

101
00:07:18,060 --> 00:07:20,940
The fate of every being

102
00:07:21,220 --> 00:07:23,060
is written in the Book of Heavenly Dao.

103
00:07:23,860 --> 00:07:24,860
Now,

104
00:07:25,060 --> 00:07:27,619
the hearts of humans, gods,
and demons are now all within you.

105
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:28,940
It is finally complete.

106
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:32,180
You will become the Heavenly Dao.

107
00:07:40,660 --> 00:07:43,540
Everything lives by its own path.

108
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:47,500
To secretly control the world

109
00:07:47,740 --> 00:07:49,739
is to take away everyone's freedom

110
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:51,180
and every possible future!

111
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:52,499
I don't want

112
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:53,980
the Book of Heavenly Dao!

113
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:55,820
To hell with your Heavenly Dao!

114
00:08:00,980 --> 00:08:02,820
You have not changed.

115
00:08:04,100 --> 00:08:05,739
From now on, this world

116
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:07,860
will have no Heavenly Dao at all.

117
00:08:08,180 --> 00:08:10,180
If any other Heavenly Dao steps in,

118
00:08:10,420 --> 00:08:13,540
this world will fall into ruin.

119
00:08:43,180 --> 00:08:46,420
I'm immortal.

120
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:49,540
I can't die!

121
00:08:49,620 --> 00:08:50,500
Then

122
00:08:51,740 --> 00:08:53,620
I'll keep killing you until you die!

123
00:09:06,300 --> 00:09:06,980
How...

124
00:09:08,180 --> 00:09:09,380
How is this possible?

125
00:09:10,700 --> 00:09:12,260
How is this possible?

126
00:09:16,020 --> 00:09:18,100
Father!

127
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:33,580
Your Highness!

128
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:39,740
Where's the Immortal?

129
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:43,980
It's over.

130
00:09:46,460 --> 00:09:47,500
Let's go home.

131
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:01,659
This is great!

132
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:02,659
I turned back!

133
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:04,340
I'm human again!

134
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:07,139
This is great! I'm human again!

135
00:10:07,140 --> 00:10:09,539
This is great!

136
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:12,699
I changed back!

137
00:10:12,700 --> 00:10:13,860
This is great!

138
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:20,500
This is great!

139
00:10:20,820 --> 00:10:22,900
This is great!

140
00:10:38,110 --> 00:10:42,180
(Sixteen years later)

141
00:11:01,940 --> 00:11:03,640
Your Majesty, there is news
from the border.

142
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,899
One man and one god
from the northern Luo State

143
00:11:04,900 --> 00:11:05,840
have crossed our border.

144
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,200
They're heading for Ning Capital.

145
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,740
They say they want to take
the Red Spider Lily.

146
00:11:11,660 --> 00:11:13,220
I'm willing to lead
the army against them!

147
00:11:13,260 --> 00:11:15,500
You think you are worthy?

148
00:11:24,420 --> 00:11:26,779
(If any other Heavenly Dao steps in, )

149
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:29,140
(this world will fall into ruin.)

150
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:31,140
Who are you people?

151
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:33,220
How dare you come here looking to die?

152
00:11:43,900 --> 00:11:45,609
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

153
00:11:45,610 --> 00:11:48,459
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

154
00:11:48,460 --> 00:11:51,199
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

155
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,829
♪Let the long shadows♪

156
00:11:52,830 --> 00:11:58,430
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

157
00:11:58,480 --> 00:12:00,079
♪If in a dream♪

158
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:02,839
♪I can hear your voice♪

159
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:05,689
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

160
00:12:05,690 --> 00:12:08,179
♪Let it be us♪

161
00:12:08,180 --> 00:12:09,019
I'm back.

162
00:12:09,020 --> 00:12:13,100
♪drawing endlessly close♪

163
00:12:24,550 --> 00:12:29,700
(The End)

164
00:12:31,260 --> 00:12:33,979
A Soft-Hearted God ends here for now.

165
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:36,069
The whole cast bows in thanks.

166
00:12:36,070 --> 00:12:37,769
Thank you for staying with us.

167
00:12:37,770 --> 00:12:40,180
See you in the next chapter.

168
00:12:43,370 --> 00:12:45,159
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

169
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:46,949
♪Chasing something always out of reach♪

170
00:12:46,950 --> 00:12:50,019
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

171
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:56,800
♪Living the same day
over and over again♪

172
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,829
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

173
00:12:58,830 --> 00:13:01,679
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

174
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:04,419
♪I'd rather this night never end♪
It's a wrap!

175
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:06,049
♪Let the long shadows♪

176
00:13:06,050 --> 00:13:11,650
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

177
00:13:11,700 --> 00:13:13,299
♪If in a dream♪

178
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:16,059
♪I can hear your voice♪

179
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:18,909
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

180
00:13:18,910 --> 00:13:21,509
♪Let it be us♪

181
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:26,299
♪drawing endlessly close♪

182
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:28,059
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

183
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:30,710
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

184
00:13:30,930 --> 00:13:33,649
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

185
00:13:33,650 --> 00:13:35,299
♪Not even in time♪

186
00:13:35,300 --> 00:13:40,959
♪to tell you how I feel♪

187
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,499
♪If the rain won't stop♪

188
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:45,249
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

189
00:13:45,250 --> 00:13:48,219
♪Let love go on♪

190
00:13:48,220 --> 00:13:50,769
♪Until forever♪

191
00:13:50,770 --> 00:13:55,420
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
